yingyinNormal.en: Obviously, not a cleaning business.
yingyinNormal.zh: 显然不是干净的生意。

yingyinNormal.en: Sheldon, he obviously had feelings for her.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿，他显然对她有感情。

yingyinNormal.en: Your Ladyship, there's obviously been a misunderstanding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 夫人，显然是出了点误会。

yingyinNormal.en: Obviously, there's unfinished business. Moriarty. I told you. Moriarty's dead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很显然，还有其他事亟待解决，莫里亚蒂。我告诉你了，莫里亚蒂已经死了。

yingyinNormal.en: Wait a minute. Wait a minute. She obviously didn't understand the question.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等等，她显然没听懂你的问题。

yingyinNormal.en: All right. Hold on. Hold on. Hold on. This is Ross, okay? He's our friend. He obviously went crazy. He obviously lost his mind.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等一下，这是罗斯，他是我们的朋友，他显然是疯了，脑筋秀逗了。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't know. I mean, she obviously has some kind of unfinished business. Sit up!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不知道，老太太显然还有什么心愿还没完成呢。坐好。

yingyinNormal.en: I've done that, Doug! Obviously, he doesn't seem to care. Underwood conceded already.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我说了，道格！他显然不在乎。安德伍德已经认输了。

yingyinNormal.en: Let me handle this, Maya. She obviously likes it quiet. Hello, book lady.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我来处理，玛雅，她显然很喜欢安静地"做事"。你好啊，看书女。

yingyinNormal.en: God, I woke the beast. Sorry. I was wrong obviously, I just, I misspoke. It's okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 天啊，野兽被我吵醒了，显然是我错了，我失言，没事了。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, I meant to tell you, the Smart Blood program is obviously still in its developmental phase.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想告诉你，智能血液程序很显然还在研发阶段。

yingyinNormal.en: Remember, he said there were only two pigs on board, but he was obviously lying.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他之前说只有两只猪在他们的船上，现在看来他显然是在撒谎。

yingyinNormal.en: No, you see, someone was supposed to take them down around New Year's, but obviously someone forgot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，某人在新年期间就应该把它拿下，她显然是忘了。

yingyinNormal.en: Obviously, Chuck's master plan is working. I can't believe you think Chuck is doing these things.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很显然，恰克的大计得逞了。真不敢相信你认为是恰克干的。

yingyinNormal.en: How'd you get this? Arrived yesterday. It's pre-beta, obviously, but it's all...
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们怎么得到这个的？昨天拿到的，显然是beta测试版，但是所有的...

yingyinNormal.en: Well, you're obviously not going to tell me what it was about. But I'm glad if it's resolved.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，你显然不打算告诉我到底是怎么了，但如果解决了，我很高兴。

yingyinNormal.en: Sweetheart, you obviously have a problem. You've chosen a boyfriend exactly like your father.
yingyinNormal.zh: 亲爱的，你显然有问题了，你居然选了一个跟你爸一模一样的男朋友。

yingyinNormal.en: It obviously made you really uncomfortable, and I guess that's my answer. There's no need to beat a dead horse.
yingyinNormal.zh: 显然那让你很不舒服，我也死心了，你没有必要落井下石。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, you're always carrying this notebook around. You obviously fancy yourself as an artist.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在，你总是随身带着你这个笔记本，显然你把自己想象成了一个艺术家。

yingyinNormal.en: Look! There's a note on the back. Loved your work. Call me a sap. She was obviously very moved.
yingyinNormal.zh: 瞧，背面有字，"喜欢你的工作，请叫我挖墙脚的"。显然她非常的感动。
